		}


		else if (template == 'ADVPRMCL'){

			letter = "<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>Date: " + returnedDate + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + compTitle + " " + compName + "<br/>" + addr1 + addr2 + "<br/>" + city + ", " + state + ", " + zip + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>Dear " + compTitle + " " + compName + ":<br/><br/>Thank you for completing the survey sent to you.  On the survey you expressed concerns that deserve our attention. It is a company goal to provide the best possible service to our customers. One way to improve our service is by listening to our policyholders and others who rely upon us.<br/><br/>Under the 'Agent Notification' section of the survey, you did not grant permission to share your name or specific responses with your agent and/or claim adjuster.  In order to address your concerns properly, we need to contact your agent and/or claim adjuster regarding the situation.  May we have your permission to do so?<br/><br/>If we do not receive your permission to contact your agent and/or claim adjuster, we will not be able to investigate this matter and provide a response to your concerns.<br/><br/>Please indicate your choice below and return this letter in the enclosed postage paid envelope.<br/><br/>_______Yes, you have my permission to contact my agent and/or claim adjuster providing my name and specific concerns expressed on the enclosed survey.<br/><br/>_______No, do not share my name or specific concerns with my agent and/or claim adjuster.  I understand I will not receive a response to my comments on the attached survey.<br/><br/>Thank you for taking the time to respond to this request.<br/><br/>Sincerely,<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + advocateName + "<br/>" + advocateTitle + "<br/>" + company + "<br/>(800) 692-6326 X30799<br/>consumeraffairs@amfam.com";

