		}


		else if (template == 'ADVPRMSL'){

			letter = "<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>Date: " + returnedDate + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + compTitle + " " + compName + "<br/>" + addr1 + addr2 + "<br/>" + city + ", " + state + ", " + zip + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>Dear " + compTitle + " " + compName + ":<br/><br/>Thank you for completing the survey sent to you.  On the survey you expressed concerns that deserve our attention. It is a company goal to provide the best possible service to our customers. One way to improve our service is by listening to our policyholders and others who rely upon us.<br/><br/>Under the 'Agent Notification' section of the survey, you did not grant permission to share your name or specific responses with your agent.  In order to address your concerns properly, we need to contact your agent regarding the situation.  May we have your permission to do so?<br/><br/>If we do not receive your permission to contact your agent, we will not be able to investigate this matter and provide a response to your concerns.<br/><br/>Please indicate your choice below and return this letter in the enclosed postage paid envelope.<br/><br/>_______Yes, you have my permission to contact my agent providing my name and specific concerns expressed on the enclosed survey.<br/><br/>_______No, do not share my name or specific concerns with my agent.  I understand I will not receive a response to my comments on the attached survey.<br/><br/>Thank you for taking the time to respond to this request.<br/><br/>Sincerely,<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + advocateName + "<br/>" + advocateTitle + "<br/>" + company + "<br/>(800) 692-6326 X30799<br/>consumeraffairs@amfam.com";

		}


		else if (template == 'ADVOPRIV'){

			letter = "<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>Date: " + returnedDate + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + address + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>RE:	Complaint File Name: " + compTitle + " " + compName + ":<br/><br/>The attached complaint/inquiry was received today.  The privacy laws require us to protect the confidentiality of non-public information relating to our consumers and others who rely upon us.  Maintaining the confidentiality of this information is important to our company.  Therefore, we are unable to send our response directly to you.<br/><br/>It is a company goal to provide the best possible service to consumers.  Even though we are unable to reply directly to you, I have asked the appropriate department to research the concerns and respond directly to the complainant within ten business days from the date of this letter.<br/><br/>Sincerely,<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + advocateName + "<br/>" + advocateTitle + "<br/>" + company + "<br/>(800) 692-6326 X30799<br/>consumeraffairs@amfam.com";

		}


		else if (template == 'ADVPRIQU'){

			letter = "<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>Date: " + returnedDate + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + address + "<br/><br/><br/><br/>RE:	Complaint File Name: " + compTitle + " " + compName + ":<br/><br/>The attached complaint/inquiry was received today.  The privacy laws require us to protect the confidentiality of non-public information relating to our consumers and others who rely upon us.  Maintaining the confidentiality of this information is important to our company.  Therefore, we are unable to send our response directly to you.<br/><br/>It is a company goal to provide the best possible service to consumers.  Even though we are unable to reply directly to you, we would like to respond to the complainant.  Your request did not provide the address of the complainant.  Please forward the complete address of the complainant or ask the complainant to contact our company directly at:<br/><br/><div align='center'>Consumer Affairs Department</div><div align='center'>American Family Insurance</div><div align='center'>6000 American Parkway</div><div align='center'>Madison, WI 53783-0001</div><br/><div align='center'>Or</div><br/><div align='center'>www.amfam.com</div><br/><br/>I have enclosed a business reply envelope for you to use to return the requested information.  I am closing our file until the complainant's address is received or the complainant contacts us directly.  Thank you for your assistance in this matter.<br/><br/>Sincerely,<br/><br/><br/><br/>" + advocateName + "<br/>" + advocateTitle + "<br/>" + company + "<br/>(800) 692-6326 X30799<br/>consumeraffairs@amfam.com";

